SUMMARY:90 Minutes FREE Arcade for all Scouts at Laserdome
DESCRIPTION:All Scouts FREE Unlimited Arcade Play\nAt Laserdome\, we’re proud to celebrate Girl Scouts and Boy Scouts who are building leadership\, citizenship\, and lifelong skills. \nTo say thank you\, we’re offering during April which is Scout Month! \nPLUS\, all Scouts get $10 off ANY pass! \nOr when you come in to play just present your uniform\, roster\, registration card\, or Scout handbook and enjoy 90 minutes of unlimited arcade play (that’s a $24.99 value!) on Tuesday-Sunday after 11am in April. \n($10 discount on passes will be applied when you pick up your pass in store!) \nIT’S A DEAL WORTH SCOUTING OUT! \n\nAdditional Fun Things for Kids To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nSummer Camps\nPetting Zoo\nRailroad Attractions\n\n\n\nFun on the Farm\nAmusement Parks\nMini Golf\n\n\n\nArcades & Video Games\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/laserdome-scouts-special/
