SUMMARY:An Egg-Stra Special Easter Deal from Laserdome
DESCRIPTION:All Easter weekend\, from Thursday 4/2 thru Monday 4/6 (egg-cept Easter Sunday\, when we’re closed) we’ve got Unlimited All Day Play for YOU for just $49.99 per person! That’s UNLIMITED Verse Immersive\, UNLIMITED Laser Tag\, and UNLIMITED Arcade play! \nCome HAVE A BLAST and save $20 at Laserdome! \nOur Verse Immersive Holographic Theater will take you to places you’ve never imagined before! \nLocated in the Dome\, this augmented reality attraction places you in the middle of a three dimensional interactive holographic story while wearing fully transparent headsets. \n\nAdditional Fun Things for Kids To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nSummer Camps\nPetting Zoo\nRailroad Attractions\n\n\n\nFun on the Farm\nAmusement Parks\nMini Golf\n\n\n\nArcades & Video Games\nZip-Lines\nEvents Calendar
