SUMMARY:Egg-stra Special Easter Event at Kitchen Kettle Village
DESCRIPTION:Make our fun family event a new Easter tradition\nAdd some magic to your Easter holiday with a visit to Kitchen Kettle Village. Enjoy a delicious buffet breakfast at the Kling House Restaurant\, an egg-cellent egg hunt\, and\, of course\, be ready to meet Yummie and the Easter Bunny. Reserve your spot today – your recipe for family fun this spring. \nSeatings are by reservation at 9:30am and 11am at The Kling House Restaurant.\n\nDelicious breakfast buffet in the Kling House Restaurant at either 9:30am-10:30am\, OR 11am-Noon\nVIP Egg Hunt after each breakfast is only open to children 10 and under who are registered for the event\nPhoto opportunities with Yummie & the Easter Bunny. Don’t forget your camera\nGoodie Bag & Egg-citing Passport of Fun with treats for the kids throughout the Village\n\n\nFamilies will love the buffet featuring:\nScrambled Eggs\nHam\nSausage\nFrench Toast Sticks\nBreakfast Potatoes\nFresh Fruit\nYogurt\nBeverages: Hot Chocolate\, Coffee\, Juice\n\nThe Easter Bunny & Yummie have lots of time to mingle with the children who come to the event. Take part in the VIP Egg Hunt\, only for those children attending the event. \nEvent Dates\nReservations at 9:30AM and 11:00AM \n\nSaturday\, March 28th\nFriday\, April 3rd\nSaturday\, April 4th
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/easter-kitchen-kettle-2/
LOCATION:Kitchen Kettle Village\, 3529 Old Philadelphia Pike\, (Route 340)\, Intercourse\, PA\, 17534\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Easter Events,Intercourse, Pennsylvania
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/Event-Easter-Breakfast-with-Yummie-.png
