SUMMARY:First Friday in Downtown Lancaster City
DESCRIPTION:Downtown Lancaster springs to life from 5 to 9 pm the First Friday of each month. \nArt galleries\, studios\, museums\, restaurants\, shops\, and attractions in downtown Lancaster stay open late while people from all over head downtown to enjoy the festive atmosphere\, dining\, art\, and entertainment. \nThe arts and entertainment are thriving in Lancaster.  Not only in Lancaster city\, but throughout Lancaster County\, too. \nEvery Friday is a special event somewhere in Lancaster County. Find out more about all the various Friday events in Lancaster County\, PA happening throughout each month. \n  \n\nEvent Calendar for Lancaster\, PA »\n(click here) \nCheck below for a calendar of the upcoming Friday events:\n\nFirst Thursdays in Manheim\nFirst Fridays in Lancaster City\nFirst Friday in Mt. Gretna\nFirst Saturday in Ephrata\nSecond Saturday in Lititz\nSecond Fridays in Elizabethtown\nThird Fridays are Music Fridays in Lancaster\nFourth Friday in Columbia\nFourth Friday in Mount Joy\n\nSee our monthly Calendar of Friday Events for descriptions of each. Or\, check our monthly Events Calendar for Lancaster County.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/first-friday-lancaster-city/2026-04-03/
