SUMMARY:Easter Celebration at the Star Barn
DESCRIPTION:Easter at The Star Barn\nSpend this Easter celebrating the greatest gift God has ever given us\, Jesus. \nDuring the Easter Celebration\, enjoy egg hunts\, a special performance by Steven Courtney\, petting zoo\, face painting\, kid’s crafts\, yard games\, food vendors\, artisan vendors\, endless photo opps\, and MORE! \n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
