SUMMARY:Easter Egg Hunt at The Barn at Paradise Station
DESCRIPTION:Gather your crew and hop on over to Paradise Station for an egg hunt on the lawn! In collaboration with our friends at the Strasburg Rail Road\, enjoy a memorable day with your family. With options for different age groups\, families will get to grab some eggs\, as well as visit with The Easter Bunny! \nEGG HUNT TIMES at PARADISE STATION \n11:30am\, 1:30pm\, 3:30pm \nPlease arrive 30 minutes prior to the egg hunt start time. This is a great option for those with accessibility needs.  \nEASTER EGG HUNT ONLY – PARKING DIRECTLY AT PARADISE STATION \nEgg Hunt and visit with the Easter Bunny. Photo opportunity\, climb the Viewing Tower\, coloring\, and more available inside on the Lower Level. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/easter-egg-hunt-barn-paradise-station/2026-04-04/
LOCATION:The Barn at Paradise Station\, 312 Paradise Lane\, Ronks\, PA\, 17572\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children & Family events,Community Interest,Easter Events,Musical Events,Outdoor Activities,Paradise,Strasburg, Pennsylvania
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/barn-at-paradise-station-events-easter-egg-hunt.jpg
